Package: devoirs
Type: Package
Title: Collects homework submissions from Quarto/HTML documents
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daniel Kaplan
Maintainer: Daniel Kaplan <dtkaplan@github.com>
Description: Supports creating multiple-choice and essay questions within Quarto/HTML. Student entries for these can be collected into a JSON object suitable for handing in via a spreadsheet such as Google Forms.
